# AI Governance Decision Simulator

Research / proof-of-concept **GenLayer Intelligent Contract** that simulates the
possible consequences of DAO governance proposals **before** they are voted on.

> The contract does **not** approve, reject, score or rank proposals.
> It only generates multiple plausible future scenarios to support human decision-making.

## Idea

Instead of asking *"Is this proposal good?"*, the system asks:

> "If this proposal is accepted, what could realistically happen over the following months?"

The contract classifies the proposal, builds a category-specific simulation prompt,
runs nondeterministic LLM generation across validators, normalizes and merges the
resulting scenarios, estimates confidence, and returns a structured consensus report.

